title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 25 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 25 2022
description:
Former U.S. prosecutor Andy McCarthy joins Clay and Buck with his Mar-a-Lago affidavit predictions. Will Garland charge Trump? Veteran, AZ GOP Congressional Candidate Eli Crane on his race to win the 2nd congressional district. C&B make a very important correction on Kim Kardashian. Clay and Buck disagree on Barack Obama's intelligence.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
